OL,3,CBeckham to be awarded knighthood in
OL,4,CKing's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FThe full list is due to be released
OL,7,Fnext week, and Beckham is expected to
OL,8,Fbe on it, as ITV News Correspondent
OL,9,FSejal Karia reports
OL,11,FFormer England football captain David
OL,12,FBeckham is to be awarded a knighthood
OL,13,Fin the King's Birthday Honours, ITV
OL,14,FNews understands.
OL,16,FThe full list is due to be released
OL,17,Fnext week, and Beckham, who made 115
OL,18,Fappearances for his country, is
OL,19,Fexpected to be on it.
