OL,3,CBeckham to be awarded knighthood in
OL,4,CKing's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FBeckham has undertaken multiple
OL,7,Fcharitable endeavours outside of
OL,8,Ffootball, including working with
OL,9,FUnicef and the King's Foundation.
OL,11,FHe began his career at Manchester
OL,12,FUnited, winning the treble of Premier
OL,13,FLeague, FA Cup and Champions League
OL,14,Ftrophies in 1999.
OL,16,FHe then moved to Real Madrid in 2003,
OL,17,Fwhere his global stardom hit new
OL,18,Fheights.
