OL,3,CBeckham to be awarded knighthood in
OL,4,CKing's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FHe also played for LA Galaxy, AC Milan
OL,7,Fand Paris Saint-Germain in a wide-
OL,8,Franging career.
OL,10,FBeckham was awarded an OBE in 2003 and
OL,11,Fhas long been touted as a recipient of
OL,12,Fa knighthood.
OL,14,FIn that same year, in an ITV
OL,15,Fdocumentary titled The Real Beckhams,
OL,16,Fhis wife Victoria joked that when
OL,17,FBeckham is knighted and she's referred
OL,18,Fto as a lady, she will "make
OL,19,Feveryone," including Beckham, call her
OL,20,Fthat.
