OL,3,CBeckham to be awarded knighthood in
OL,4,CKing's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FBeckham played a key role in securing
OL,7,Fthe Olympic Games for London in 2012,
OL,8,Fand speculation that Beckham was in
OL,9,Fline for a knighthood grew after he
OL,10,Fannounced his retirement from football
OL,11,Fin 2013.
OL,13,FIn 2014, it was reported that Beckham
OL,14,Fwas on the verge of receiving a
OL,15,Fknighthood, but HM Revenue and Customs
OL,16,Fplaced a red flag on his nomination
OL,17,Fdue to his involvement in an alleged
OL,18,Ftax avoidance scheme.
