OL,3,CBeckham to be awarded knighthood in
OL,4,CKing's Birthday Honours
OL,6,FIn 2017, a series of leaked emails
OL,7,Fappeared to show Beckham criticising
OL,8,Fthe honours system and the honours
OL,9,Fcommittee.
OL,11,FBeckham said these emails were
OL,12,F"hacked", "doctored" and "private".
OL,14,FBeckham is a Goodwill Ambassador for
OL,15,FUnicef and launched the David Beckham
OL,16,FUnicef fund in 2015.
OL,18,FHe joined the King's Foundation as an
OL,19,Fambassador in 2024, working for the
OL,20,FKing's charity to further their
OL,21,Feducation programme.
